keywords:
  - fixed charge
  - global U(1) charge
  - charged vacuum decay
  - twisted Euclidean boundary conditions
  - independent Euclidean fields
  - residual twist eta0
  - fixed-Q bounce
  - homogeneous charged medium
  - Euclidean saddle
  - Minkowski continuation
  - terminal wall velocity

